## Private Member Attributes

### FastID {#a42f3fbb25e2e77466ae173bb0d3bb436}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype="FoldingSetNodeIDRef llvm::SDVTListNode::FastID">
A reference to an Interned <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/foldingsetnodeid">FoldingSetNodeID</a> for this node.

The Allocator in <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/selectiondag">SelectionDAG</a> holds the data. <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/sdvtlist">SDVTList</a> contains all types which are frequently accessed in <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/selectiondag">SelectionDAG</a>. The size of this list is not expected to be big so it won&#39;t introduce a memory penalty.

Definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/codegen/selectiondag-h/#l00107">107</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/codegen/selectiondag-h">SelectionDAG.h</a>.
</MemberDefinition>
